<view class="page">
  <view class="map-wrap">
    <map
      id="campusMap"
      class="map"
      latitude="{{latitude}}"
      longitude="{{longitude}}"
      scale="{{scale}}"
      min-scale="3"
      max-scale="20"
      enable-zoom="{{true}}"
      enable-scroll="{{true}}"
      markers="{{markers}}"
      show-location="{{showLocation}}"
      bindmarkertap="onMarkerTap"
      bindtap="onMapTap"
      bindregionchange="onRegionChange"
    >
      <cover-view class="zoom-stack">
        <cover-view class="zoom-fab" catchtap="onZoomIn">
          <cover-view class="zoom-fab-text">+</cover-view>
        </cover-view>
        <cover-view class="zoom-fab" catchtap="onZoomOut">
          <cover-view class="zoom-fab-text">−</cover-view>
        </cover-view>
      </cover-view>
    </map>
  </view>
  <view class="panel">
    <text class="panel-tip">双指捏合可缩放；亦可点右侧 +/−。点击地图任意处：自动匹配最近的校园标注（约 {{maxSnapM}} 米内）；或直接点标注图标。</text>
    <text class="panel-sub">坐标系 GCJ-02，与「腾讯位置服务」拾取一致。</text>
    <button class="btn-back" bindtap="onCancel">取消</button>
  </view>
</view>
